<section id="demo" class="demo">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-label">Demo</h2>
    <h3 class="section-title">One command. No API key required.</h3>
    <p class="caption">
      A real <code>npx mythos-agent quick</code> against a vulnerable fixture.
      Pattern scan runs in ~10&nbsp;ms, offline, no config.
    </p>

    <figure class="figure">
      <img
        src="/demo.gif"
        alt="Terminal running npx mythos-agent quick against a vulnerable fixture. The scanner returns 13 findings in 10 milliseconds, highlighting five critical and high-severity issues with file:line pointers and a suggested auto-fix command."
