        height="720"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <figcaption>
        Transcript: <code>npx mythos-agent quick</code> → scanned 47 files in 10&nbsp;ms →
        5 findings visible with file:line pointers → auto-fix hint. 13 total findings.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

